---
title: Fiery Lentil Spaghetti Arrabiata with Spinach and Roasted Red Peppers
description: There's nothing boring about this dinner! Lentils and tomatoes are the base of a sauce that's jazzed up with garlic, chili flakes and chili sauce. Penne acts as the perfect pasta shape to capture all the sauce!
